<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.10">
<l>poruntiya māmaru tiṉṉiṭai pōyavem</l>
<l>peruntakā yuṉkaḻal kāṇiya pētuṟṟu</l>
<l>varuntināṉ vācaka mālaikoṇ ṭuṉṉaiyē</l>
<l>yiruntirun tettaṉai kālam pulampuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O our paragon who went in between the united great Marutu trees,</l>
<l>confusedly suffering in order to see your anklet,</l>
<l>being [and] being there with a word garland,</l>
<l>how many times will I lament you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
